metadata.title: STMK Dog Birthday Outfit, Dog Birthday Bandana Girl with Dog Birthday Number Hat Bowtie Tutu Skirt Cake Toy Lets Pawty Paw Balloons Dog Happy Birthday Banner for Dog Puppy Birthday Party Supplies
features: DOG BIRTHDAY PARTY SUPPLIES: This dog birthday outfit set includes a dog birthday bandana printed with BIRTHDAY GIRL, a cute dog birthday hat, a dog birthday tutu skirt, a dog squeaky birthday cake toy, a set of 0-8 birthday numbers, a dog bowtie, 10 paw balloons, LETS PAWTY letters balloons and a dog birthday banner printed with HAPPY BIRTHDAY. This suit can meet all your needs and bring some surprises to your furry pets.

SIZE: Dog birthday bandana size: 28" x 19" x 19", the adjustable bandana is suitable for dogs with a neck circumference less than 24" and greater than 14". Dog birthday hat size：The hat with an adjustable elastic cord is about 4" high and about 4.5" in diameter. The bowtie adjustable length from 7" to 12.5". Tutu skirt is suitable for dogs with a waist size of 15''-35''. Paw balloons size: 12". LETS PAWTY letters balloons size: 16". Birthday banner length: 48".

HIGH-QUALITY: The birthday bandanna is made of cotton fabric, comfortable and durable. Dog birthday hat is made of high-quality pressure-resistant fabric and pompon, which can be reused. High-quality Tutu skirts are made of durable soft gauze and ribbons. The squeaky dog birthday cake toy is made of soft fabric, squeezing the cake will make funny squeaking noises to attract the dog's attention.

EXCLUSIVE CUSTOM BIRTHDAY HAT: We provide you with 10 shiny birthday age numbers and 20 glue points. You can paste the corresponding birthday age numbers on the dog birthday hat according to the age of your cute pet. Your careful preparation can definitely make your pet a highly anticipated point, allowing you and your family and friends to enjoy a happy birthday party.

GREAT DOG BIRTHDAY GIFT: High quality dog birthday party supplies can be used for your pet at every birthday time. This set is a great birthday gift for your furry pet. Let this birthday be the most memorable moment in a dog's life.
